00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:03.610
Another foundational concept is cohesion, which is the extent to which

00:00:03.610 --> 00:00:07.480
a module has a single purpose. You would like the cohesion of your module to

00:00:07.480 --> 00:00:12.540
be high in order to enhance its understandability and promote its reuse.

00:00:12.540 --> 00:00:16.480
Cohesion as a software design principle was also invented by Larry Constantine.

